    "description": "此課程是進入大四畢業專題前的熱身，上課的同學必須分組進行小專題的專案討論及製作，最終發表小專題影片成果。內容可以是2D動畫、3D動畫、停格動畫等各種類型的影片，各組至少需要找一位視傳系老師指導作品。<br>This course is a warm-up before entering the senior graduation project. Students in the class must be divided into groups to discuss and produce small-topic projects, and finally publish the results of small-topic videos. The content can be 2D animation, 3D animation, stop-motion animation and other types of films. Each group needs to find at least one teacher from the Department of Visual Communication Design to guide the work.",
    "prerequisites": "建議具有動畫組劇本寫作及分鏡基礎能力；並至少修過以下其中一種類型（2D、3D或停格動畫）課程及具有影音製作經驗。",
